entries.arrived_at_delivery: Stand by for arrival of transport. Once it arrives, dock with the transport and make the trade.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: And there we go. We have what we want, and you have what you want.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Hold her steady while my crew transfers the cargo.
entries.failed_destroyed: Now we are going to have to do this all over again. I am going to lose my shirt on this deal.
entries.found_loc_d: Good...now meet the Harkon ship to exchange the computer chips for the blaster crystals.
entries.hello_d: Hey there, you must be the pilot with my load of chips. Go ahead and dock whenever you are ready.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Trade the computer control chips for the blaster crystals.
entries.quest_location_d: A Harkon company freighter will meet you in the Corellian system.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the freighter in order to make the exchange.
entries.split_quest_alert: Now onto the last step. The blaster crystals are for Nym's boys in the Lok system so get there and wait for further instructions.
entries.title: Corellian System: Smuggling for the Trandoshans Part II
entries.title_d: Fezrik has hired you to run several tasks in order to get the Trandoshan slavers a load of glitterdust. You now need to trade the computer control chips for a load of blaster crystals.
